data.description: Wow! Beautiful corner-lot property that is located within minutes of Ft. Liberty (Bragg).  The area is a great place to raise children.  There is a front porch to star gaze and sunporch in the back for entertaining guest. This property has 4 bedrooms and two additional finished upstairs rooms that can be used as additional bedrooms, office space, or hangout areas. The additional finished rooms each have optimal closet space. This home has vaulted ceilings. There is a huge master bedroom downstairs with walk-in closet. The master bedroom has tray ceiling. After a long day and for your enjoyment, there is a jetted tub to relax in.  The backyard is fenced-in so no need to rush home to let out the dog. In the backyard there is also a storge house. The beautiful kitchen has granite countertops and ceramic tile for the flooring. Did I forget to mention that both A/C units were replaced in 2022. The water heater and refrigerator were replaced this year (2023).  Schedule an appointment today.
